The paper focuses on the communication between robotic systems and the control center, which is a key aspect of robotics (cs.RO). The proposed solution involves buffer management, which is related to network infrastructure (cs.NI) and distributed computing (cs.DC). The paper also mentions the use of an evaluation function, which is a common technique in artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the paper discusses the application scenarios of exploration, rescue operations, and surveillance, which are related to systems and control (cs.SY).
